00:14:19,440 --> 00:14:20,840
I wish you good business.

289
00:14:21,840 --> 00:14:22,880
Thank you.

290
00:14:25,400 --> 00:14:26,800
Why did that sound like a curse?

291
00:14:30,160 --> 00:14:31,160
Really?

292
00:14:32,160 --> 00:14:34,400
What if he confesses to you?

293
00:14:35,000 --> 00:14:37,080
I don't think I will accept it.

294
00:14:37,160 --> 00:14:38,080
What about you?

295
00:14:38,160 --> 00:14:39,800
If a close friend confesses to you,

296
00:14:39,880 --> 00:14:41,080
what would you do?

297
00:14:44,040 --> 00:14:46,040
I won't date a close friend either.

298
00:14:46,120 --> 00:14:48,560
I think it's not easy being friends.

299
00:14:48,640 --> 00:14:50,400
What if something happens

300
00:14:50,480 --> 00:14:51,480
after we start dating?

301
00:14:51,560 --> 00:14:53,920
It'll be awkward
if we can't be friends anymore.

302
00:14:54,000 --> 00:14:55,080
You are right.

303
00:14:58,960 --> 00:15:00,000
Gu Ran.

304
00:15:00,840 --> 00:15:01,960
What a coincidence.

305
00:15:02,040 --> 00:15:03,560
You can buy us ice cream.

306
00:15:05,080 --> 00:15:06,080
Let me say this first.

307
00:15:06,160 --> 00:15:07,720
I'm only treating Fu Yao and the others.

308
00:15:07,800 --> 00:15:09,200
You got lucky to be here.

309
00:15:09,800 --> 00:15:11,360
You're so petty.

310
00:15:17,640 --> 00:15:19,040
There are no clouds tonight.

311
00:15:19,120 --> 00:15:20,680
I'm sure the fireworks will be pretty.

312
00:15:22,440 --> 00:15:24,320
It should be a while
until the fireworks display.

313
00:15:25,360 --> 00:15:26,600
Let's play a game.

314
00:15:26,680 --> 00:15:27,560
Sure.

315
00:15:28,040 --> 00:15:30,760
There's a game going viral online.

316
00:15:30,840 --> 00:15:32,160
Let me give you a test.

317
00:15:32,240 --> 00:15:33,480
The rule is simple.

318
00:15:33,560 --> 00:15:35,560
Use three words to form a sentence.

319
00:15:37,240 --> 00:15:38,080
All right.

320
00:15:43,240 --> 00:15:44,240
First challenge.

321
00:15:44,320 --> 00:15:45,680
"Su Zaizai,"

322
00:15:45,760 --> 00:15:47,720
"Susu," and "cute."

323
00:15:50,720 --> 00:15:52,120
"Su Zaizai

324
00:15:52,600 --> 00:15:54,560
is jealous that Susu is cuter than her."

325
00:15:55,360 --> 00:15:56,440
What?

326
00:15:56,520 --> 00:15:57,440
It should obviously be,

327
00:15:57,520 --> 00:15:59,160
"Su Zaizai is cuter than Susu."

328
00:15:59,720 --> 00:16:01,200
You could also say,

329
00:16:01,280 --> 00:16:02,200
"Su Zaizai is

330
00:16:02,280 --> 00:16:03,440
just as cute as Susu."

331
00:16:03,920 --> 00:16:04,800
Second challenge.

332
00:16:04,880 --> 00:16:08,240
"Every day," "see," and "cake."

333
00:16:08,320 --> 00:16:11,000
"If you eat cake every day,

334
00:16:11,080 --> 00:16:12,520
you will see the doctor."

335
00:16:13,760 --> 00:16:15,920
You are not wrong.

336
00:16:16,000 --> 00:16:18,080
But the first sentence I think of is,

337
00:16:18,160 --> 00:16:20,240
"Seeing you every day

338
00:16:20,320 --> 00:16:22,120
is as sweet as eating cake."

339
00:16:26,720 --> 00:16:28,320
Third challenge.

340
00:16:28,400 --> 00:16:31,320
"Susu," "jelly," and "angry."

341
00:16:33,840 --> 00:16:35,040
"Susu

342
00:16:35,760 --> 00:16:37,360
ate my jelly,

343
00:16:37,440 --> 00:16:38,800
so I'm angry."

344
00:16:39,680 --> 00:16:41,560
You are so petty.

345
00:16:43,760 --> 00:16:45,640
Wait, I keep making the challenges.

346
00:16:45,720 --> 00:16:46,800
You should come up with one.

347
00:16:46,880 --> 00:16:48,520
But let me warn you.

348
00:16:48,600 --> 00:16:50,040
I'm really good at this game.

349
00:16:50,120 --> 00:16:52,240
You can give me a difficult one.

350
00:17:00,080 --> 00:17:01,480
"Zhang Lurang,"

351
00:17:01,560 --> 00:17:02,440
"like,"

352
00:17:03,960 --> 00:17:04,920
"Su Zaizai."

353
00:17:14,599 --> 00:17:15,800
Do you think

354
00:17:16,720 --> 00:17:18,079
I have always been confident

355
00:17:18,160 --> 00:17:19,480
in everything I do?

356
00:17:21,000 --> 00:17:21,880
Yes.

357
00:17:22,640 --> 00:17:23,800
That's not entirely true.

358
00:17:24,599 --> 00:17:25,640
For example,

359
00:17:26,560 --> 00:17:28,200
when I confess this to you.

360
00:17:29,680 --> 00:17:32,480
Confess what?

361
00:17:35,000 --> 00:17:36,000
I like you.

362
00:18:07,040 --> 00:18:09,240
I think we can check our scores tomorrow.

363
00:18:12,560 --> 00:18:13,520
Are you nervous?

364
00:18:14,840 --> 00:18:16,120
Nervous?

365
00:18:17,240 --> 00:18:19,000
What is there to be nervous about?

366
00:18:19,080 --> 00:18:21,160
It's just dating.

367
00:18:24,400 --> 00:18:25,640
I'm talking about

368
00:18:26,520 --> 00:18:27,560
checking our scores.

369
00:18:31,080 --> 00:18:34,320
I don't think there should be a problem.

370
00:18:43,360 --> 00:18:45,440
Don't you usually have a lot to say?

371
00:18:45,520 --> 00:18:46,560
Why are you

372
00:18:46,640 --> 00:18:47,840
so quiet today?

373
00:18:49,600 --> 00:18:52,920
I usually don't speak much.

374
00:18:55,640 --> 00:18:57,800
I remember there is a food street

375
00:18:57,880 --> 00:19:00,040
behind East China University

376
00:19:00,120 --> 00:19:01,440
that is quite famous.

377
00:19:01,520 --> 00:19:02,880
It's worth checking out.

378
00:19:03,440 --> 00:19:04,320
Let's go together.

379
00:19:46,240 --> 00:19:48,440
I'm in a relationship with Rangrang!

380
00:19:49,080 --> 00:19:51,400
I'm not dreaming, am I?

381
00:19:54,200 --> 00:19:56,000
Calm down, Su Zaizai.

382
00:19:56,080 --> 00:19:57,800
Isn't this normal?

383
00:19:57,880 --> 00:19:58,960
Don't be so excited.

384
00:19:59,040 --> 00:20:00,800
I'm sure Rangrang is incredibly calm.

385
00:20:05,480 --> 00:20:07,240
<i>Rangrang, are you asleep?</i>

386
00:20:09,920 --> 00:20:11,600
Lurang, pour me a glass too.

387
00:20:28,200 --> 00:20:29,520
Lurang.

388
00:20:30,280 --> 00:20:31,280
Lurang!

389
00:20:32,040 --> 00:20:33,320
Why are you so happy?

390
00:20:34,200 --> 00:20:36,720
Did something happy happen to you?

391
00:20:41,360 --> 00:20:42,560
Water!

392
00:20:54,240 --> 00:20:56,120
<i>Rangrang, are you asleep?</i>

393
00:21:00,920 --> 00:21:02,440
<i>I don't think</i>

394
00:21:02,520 --> 00:21:03,520
<i>I can sleep.</i>

395
00:21:21,080 --> 00:21:22,120
What time is it?

396
00:21:22,680 --> 00:21:23,760
There are ten seconds to go.

397
00:21:23,840 --> 00:21:26,040
Seven, six,

398
00:21:26,120 --> 00:21:28,320
five, four,

399
00:21:28,400 --> 00:21:30,520
three, two, one.

400
00:21:30,600 --> 00:21:32,000
-You can check it now. Hurry.
-Hurry.

401
00:21:38,880 --> 00:21:39,920
SU ZAIZAI'S TOTAL SCORE, 586

402
00:21:40,960 --> 00:21:42,360
I got 586!

403
00:21:42,440 --> 00:21:45,040
Dad, I've never scored so high!

404
00:21:45,120 --> 00:21:47,520
Mom, pinch me! Quickly!

405
00:21:49,480 --> 00:21:50,720
No need for pinching.

406
00:21:50,800 --> 00:21:51,920
My daughter is the best!

407
00:21:52,000 --> 00:21:53,880
I must call your homeroom teacher.

408
00:21:53,960 --> 00:21:55,640
He asked about your results this morning.

409
00:21:56,280 --> 00:21:57,160
I'll buy groceries.

410
00:21:57,240 --> 00:21:58,200
We'll celebrate tonight.

411
00:22:07,320 --> 00:22:09,640
<i>Rangrang, I can go
to East China University!</i>

412
00:22:20,680 --> 00:22:23,760
Did Rangrang get a bad score?

413
00:22:24,320 --> 00:22:25,720
<i>I'm downstairs.</i>

414
00:22:29,160 --> 00:22:30,120
Rangrang!

415
00:22:35,000 --> 00:22:37,840
Did you check your results too?

416
00:22:40,080 --> 00:22:41,480
I thought about it.

417
00:22:41,560 --> 00:22:42,640
Which university we go to

418
00:22:42,720 --> 00:22:44,640
isn't that important.

419
00:22:44,720 --> 00:22:46,680
The distance is not a problem.

420
00:22:46,760 --> 00:22:47,600
I can...

421
00:22:47,680 --> 00:22:50,520
I think the boys' dorm and girls' dorm

422
00:22:50,600 --> 00:22:51,480
aren't that far apart.

423
00:22:52,600 --> 00:22:53,840
Rangrang!

424
00:22:58,520 --> 00:23:00,040
Your four years at university

425
00:23:00,120 --> 00:23:01,160
are all mine.

426
00:23:01,240 --> 00:23:02,280
Zhang Lurang,

427
00:23:02,360 --> 00:23:03,480
what do you think about that?

428
00:23:05,680 --> 00:23:06,520
I'm honored.

429
00:23:06,600 --> 00:23:09,320
Before school starts, I'll write down
all the things I want to do with you

430
00:23:09,400 --> 00:23:11,240
and complete them one by one.

431
00:23:12,120 --> 00:23:13,200
What is the first thing?

432
00:23:14,840 --> 00:23:15,840
Watch the sunrise.

433
00:23:17,600 --> 00:23:19,240
We don't have to wait for school to start.

434
00:23:19,320 --> 00:23:20,200
Let's go together.

435
00:23:21,640 --> 00:23:22,680
Watch the sunrise.

436
00:23:30,240 --> 00:23:31,240
No.

437
00:23:54,600 --> 00:23:56,440
A date between two people.

438
00:24:10,760 --> 00:24:11,920
This is the perfect time.

439
00:24:12,000 --> 00:24:13,720
We might even be able to rent a good tent.

440
00:24:13,800 --> 00:24:14,680
Let's go.

441
00:24:17,040 --> 00:24:17,960
Well...

442
00:24:19,200 --> 00:24:20,040
What's wrong?

443
00:24:20,600 --> 00:24:22,760
Hurry!

444
00:24:22,840 --> 00:24:24,000
Help me put together the lamp.

445
00:24:24,080 --> 00:24:26,120
How can you camp without this?

446
00:24:29,080 --> 00:24:30,600
Gu...

447
00:24:30,680 --> 00:24:32,200
Gu Ran?

448
00:24:32,280 --> 00:24:33,960
When did you develop a stutter?

449
00:24:35,680 --> 00:24:37,480
He happened to come to my house

450
00:24:37,560 --> 00:24:38,800
and saw me packing.

451
00:24:40,160 --> 00:24:42,320
I knew you wanted to give us a surprise,

452
00:24:42,400 --> 00:24:43,880
but advance notice is better

453
00:24:43,960 --> 00:24:45,080
when it comes to camping,

454
00:24:45,160 --> 00:24:46,240
so we can prepare properly.

455
00:24:47,080 --> 00:24:49,160
Did you say "us"?

456
00:24:50,680 --> 00:24:51,800
Zaizai!

457
00:25:01,720 --> 00:25:02,880
When Gu Ran told me,

458
00:25:02,960 --> 00:25:04,200
I knew he would spoil your plan.

459
00:25:04,280 --> 00:25:06,240
It's okay. I'm here. I'll get rid of him.

460
00:25:06,320 --> 00:25:07,960
What a relief.

461
00:25:10,040 --> 00:25:11,240
Let's go then.

462
00:25:11,320 --> 00:25:13,480
Hold on. We're waiting on someone.

463
00:25:41,800 --> 00:25:43,240
If I hadn't come,

464
00:25:43,320 --> 00:25:45,240
all of you would have suffered.

465
00:25:47,120 --> 00:25:48,040
{\an8}Don't move.

466
00:25:48,840 --> 00:25:50,240
{\an8}-What are you looking at?
-Be still.

467
00:25:50,840 --> 00:25:51,720
Tell me.

468
00:25:52,240 --> 00:25:53,720
How can anyone be so blind?

469
00:25:58,160 --> 00:25:59,320
Here you go.

470
00:26:03,320 --> 00:26:04,360
Gu Ran.

471
00:26:06,120 --> 00:26:08,320
I need help here. Come and help me.

472
00:26:14,560 --> 00:26:15,480
As expected,

473
00:26:16,240 --> 00:26:18,280
with great power
comes great responsibility.

474
00:26:20,440 --> 00:26:21,360
I'm going there.

475
00:26:21,440 --> 00:26:22,400
Call me if you need me.

476
00:26:46,960 --> 00:26:48,600
{\an8}I'm not in a bad mood.

477
00:26:49,360 --> 00:26:50,560
{\an8}I just want to make you happy.

478
00:26:55,360 --> 00:26:57,320
Are we going to look at the stars tonight?

479
00:26:58,080 --> 00:26:58,920
Sure.

480
00:27:07,080 --> 00:27:09,560
I didn't expect the stars here
to be so pretty.

481
00:27:10,360 --> 00:27:12,800
Why didn't I ever realize
the stars were so big?

482
00:27:20,400 --> 00:27:21,280
Gu Ran.

483
00:27:22,440 --> 00:27:24,480
Jiang Jia? Are you here to stargaze too?

484
00:27:25,040 --> 00:27:26,440
<i>You look like a star yourself.</i>

485
00:27:28,040 --> 00:27:30,280
I just realized my lamp is broken.

486
00:27:30,360 --> 00:27:31,680
I'm sure you can fix it

487
00:27:31,760 --> 00:27:32,720
since you are so great.

488
00:27:37,400 --> 00:27:38,520
You have a good taste.

489
00:27:47,440 --> 00:27:48,600
Lead the way,

490
00:27:48,680 --> 00:27:49,560
Xiaojiazi.

491
00:28:05,920 --> 00:28:07,080
It's my first time

492
00:28:08,840 --> 00:28:10,120
finding Gu Ran so annoying.

493
00:28:23,000 --> 00:28:25,200
{\an8}I'm surprised. You can actually fix it.

494
00:28:26,840 --> 00:28:28,440
{\an8}There is plenty that you don't know.

495
00:28:29,720 --> 00:28:30,760
Well?

496
00:28:30,840 --> 00:28:32,200
Don't you find me handsome now?

497
00:28:33,000 --> 00:28:34,280
How narcissistic.

498
00:28:35,840 --> 00:28:37,080
Give me that.

499
00:28:56,480 --> 00:28:57,400
Your hair is messy.

500
00:29:06,680 --> 00:29:08,480
When I'm not around in the future,

501
00:29:08,560 --> 00:29:10,600
who will help you when you're so clumsy?

502
00:29:10,680 --> 00:29:13,200
You won't be going too far anyway.

503
00:29:18,160 --> 00:29:19,360
I'm going abroad.

504
00:29:19,440 --> 00:29:20,960
Even if you are going abroad...

505
00:29:31,040 --> 00:29:33,920
Is this another joke?

506
00:29:34,000 --> 00:29:35,360
This is not funny.

507
00:29:36,880 --> 00:29:37,720
No.

508
00:29:38,240 --> 00:29:40,080
I discussed it with my parents

509
00:29:40,160 --> 00:29:41,240
for a long time.

510
00:29:41,840 --> 00:29:44,280
This foreign exchange opportunity
is very important.

511
00:29:44,840 --> 00:29:45,960
I want to check it out.

512
00:29:48,960 --> 00:29:49,840
Then

513
00:29:50,680 --> 00:29:52,120
that's great.

514
00:29:56,960 --> 00:29:58,400
Then

515
00:29:58,480 --> 00:30:00,560
have you told Zhang Lurang and the others?

516
00:30:01,320 --> 00:30:02,440
Not yet.

517
00:30:02,520 --> 00:30:03,400
Maybe in a few days.

518
00:30:05,840 --> 00:30:07,200
I'm sure they will be shocked

519
00:30:07,280 --> 00:30:08,360
when they find out.

520
00:30:10,960 --> 00:30:11,800
{\an8}Slow down.

521
00:30:16,520 --> 00:30:17,440
What's up?

522
00:30:18,240 --> 00:30:19,360
I'm so happy.

523
00:30:19,440 --> 00:30:20,920
It feels a bit unreal.

524
00:30:21,520 --> 00:30:23,200
You can't escape if I hold your hand.

525
00:30:23,280 --> 00:30:24,600
This is more reassuring.

526
00:30:30,920 --> 00:30:31,800
Don't.

527
00:30:32,680 --> 00:30:34,000
Aren't you cold?

528
00:30:35,920 --> 00:30:37,880
This development is too fast.

529
00:30:38,520 --> 00:30:40,000
It's like a dream.

530
00:30:43,320 --> 00:30:44,680
Su Zaizai.

531
00:30:44,760 --> 00:30:47,520
I know you want me to act normal again.

532
00:30:52,040 --> 00:30:52,960
Come inside.

533
00:30:55,960 --> 00:30:57,760
My Rangrang is so smart.

534
00:30:57,840 --> 00:30:59,680
I don't feel cold like this.

535
00:31:09,240 --> 00:31:11,080
Is the toilet over here?

536
00:31:24,800 --> 00:31:25,880
After I go abroad,

537
00:31:25,960 --> 00:31:28,040
I don't know when we will meet again.

538
00:31:29,280 --> 00:31:30,600
-I...
-Gu Ran!

539
00:31:35,840 --> 00:31:37,640
Were you talking in secret?

540
00:31:37,720 --> 00:31:38,920
What is it? Let me hear it too.

541
00:31:40,320 --> 00:31:41,200
It's nothing.

542
00:31:41,280 --> 00:31:42,680
Gu Ran was helping me fix the lamp.

543
00:31:42,760 --> 00:31:44,040
What's up?

544
00:31:47,520 --> 00:31:48,800
What did I want to tell you?

545
00:31:50,440 --> 00:31:51,520
That's right!

546
00:31:52,320 --> 00:31:53,400
Let me tell you.

547
00:31:53,480 --> 00:31:55,520
Something is wrong with this place.

548
00:31:55,600 --> 00:31:58,720
I just saw two people hugging outside.

549
00:31:58,800 --> 00:32:00,320
When I looked more closely,

550
00:32:01,640 --> 00:32:04,360
it looked like a person with two heads.

551
00:32:04,840 --> 00:32:06,280
That's so scary.

552
00:32:08,320 --> 00:32:09,400
Something is wrong indeed.

553
00:32:11,040 --> 00:32:12,400
Something is wrong with you here.

554
00:32:12,480 --> 00:32:14,440
Do you not believe me?

555
00:32:14,520 --> 00:32:16,040
I saw it clearly.

556
00:32:16,120 --> 00:32:17,600
That person

557
00:32:17,680 --> 00:32:20,040
was wearing a black jacket.

558
00:32:21,080 --> 00:32:22,120
It was like this one.

559
00:32:22,200 --> 00:32:23,920
The other head

560
00:32:24,000 --> 00:32:25,080
was a female

561
00:32:25,160 --> 00:32:28,000
with very long hair,

562
00:32:28,080 --> 00:32:29,280
about as long as hers.

563
00:32:40,960 --> 00:32:41,880
I made a mistake.

564
00:32:42,520 --> 00:32:43,360
I saw nothing.

565
00:32:44,040 --> 00:32:45,480
I didn't see anything.

566
00:32:46,280 --> 00:32:47,400
I made a mistake.

567
00:32:47,480 --> 00:32:50,200
Well, it's late. Go back to sleep.

568
00:32:50,280 --> 00:32:52,040
We need to watch the sunrise tomorrow.

569
00:32:52,120 --> 00:32:54,000
-Yes, let's go.
-Let's go.

570
00:32:59,960 --> 00:33:00,920
Then

571
00:33:03,280 --> 00:33:04,160
I'm going back too.

572
00:33:06,320 --> 00:33:07,200
Okay.

