00:33:13,640 --> 00:33:14,840
What's wrong with them?

574
00:33:16,720 --> 00:33:17,840
They suffered a shock.

575
00:33:28,520 --> 00:33:29,880
Don't you have anything to say?

576
00:33:29,960 --> 00:33:31,320
When did it happen?

577
00:33:32,520 --> 00:33:33,480
You even hid it

578
00:33:33,560 --> 00:33:34,600
from me.

579
00:33:35,200 --> 00:33:36,080
Did I?

580
00:33:36,720 --> 00:33:37,640
You...

581
00:33:39,040 --> 00:33:39,880
Not really.

582
00:33:43,280 --> 00:33:44,360
You can date,

583
00:33:44,440 --> 00:33:45,800
but you must promise me one thing.

584
00:33:48,160 --> 00:33:51,440
You must never tell my grandma this.

585
00:33:53,280 --> 00:33:54,400
I can foresee

586
00:33:54,480 --> 00:33:56,000
how hard it will be for me to date.

587
00:33:56,640 --> 00:33:58,840
If my grandma
finds out you have a girlfriend now,

588
00:33:58,920 --> 00:34:00,280
she will be disappointed with me

589
00:34:00,360 --> 00:34:01,560
and torture me more.

590
00:34:03,880 --> 00:34:05,120
I'm serious about this.

591
00:34:05,200 --> 00:34:06,920
Why are you playing on your phone?

592
00:34:08,239 --> 00:34:09,360
I'm telling her good night.

593
00:34:12,520 --> 00:34:14,520
I can't continue this conversation
for a second more.

594
00:34:39,880 --> 00:34:40,880
<i>I'm going abroad.</i>

595
00:34:46,520 --> 00:34:49,320
Is this another joke?

596
00:34:49,400 --> 00:34:50,639
This is not funny.

597
00:34:52,239 --> 00:34:53,080
No.

598
00:34:53,840 --> 00:34:55,360
I discussed it with my parents

599
00:34:55,440 --> 00:34:56,560
for a long time.

600
00:34:56,639 --> 00:34:59,080
This foreign exchange opportunity
is very important.

601
00:34:59,640 --> 00:35:00,640
I want to check it out.

602
00:35:10,880 --> 00:35:13,120
It's my first time waking up so early

603
00:35:13,200 --> 00:35:14,400
just to watch the sunrise.

604
00:35:16,480 --> 00:35:17,920
I suddenly realized

605
00:35:18,000 --> 00:35:19,960
that we've seen many sunsets before.

606
00:35:20,040 --> 00:35:21,520
Now we've watched the sunrise today.

607
00:35:21,600 --> 00:35:23,600
Are we ending what we started?

608
00:35:24,400 --> 00:35:25,320
Touch wood.

609
00:35:25,800 --> 00:35:28,080
We still have a long way to go.

610
00:35:28,160 --> 00:35:29,040
This is not the end.

611
00:35:34,880 --> 00:35:35,720
You are right.

612
00:35:35,800 --> 00:35:36,760
It's not over yet.

613
00:35:39,200 --> 00:35:40,720
The exam results are out.

614
00:35:40,800 --> 00:35:42,400
Have you decided on your schools?

615
00:35:45,120 --> 00:35:46,400
Both of us applied
for East China University.

616
00:35:47,120 --> 00:35:48,560
So you've been planning it.

617
00:35:49,440 --> 00:35:50,320
What about you?

618
00:35:51,840 --> 00:35:52,840
Me?

619
00:35:53,880 --> 00:35:56,080
Do you remember Yong'an?
We visited before.

620
00:35:56,160 --> 00:35:57,640
I'll be there for four years.

621
00:35:57,720 --> 00:35:59,160
Way to go.

622
00:36:00,040 --> 00:36:01,360
Yong'an University is famous

623
00:36:01,440 --> 00:36:02,600
for its economics program.

624
00:36:02,680 --> 00:36:05,200
Of course. Who do you think I am?

625
00:36:05,280 --> 00:36:06,320
Seriously!

626
00:36:15,040 --> 00:36:16,280
The sun is coming out.

627
00:36:30,320 --> 00:36:31,400
This is great.

628
00:36:32,200 --> 00:36:33,640
We all have our own goals

629
00:36:33,720 --> 00:36:35,440
and directions to work hard toward.

630
00:36:35,520 --> 00:36:37,560
I hope the next time
we watch the sunrise together,

631
00:36:37,640 --> 00:36:39,880
we will have become better people.

632
00:36:42,280 --> 00:36:43,280
We will.

633
00:36:54,160 --> 00:36:55,640
The next time we meet,

634
00:36:55,720 --> 00:36:58,200
we'll say, "It has been a long time!"

635
00:37:01,680 --> 00:37:03,920
Go farther

636
00:37:04,000 --> 00:37:05,760
and see a brighter light!

637
00:37:07,720 --> 00:37:12,320
The sunrise is so beautiful!

638
00:37:32,160 --> 00:37:35,120
TO JIANG JIA

639
00:37:43,840 --> 00:37:45,840
<i>You didn't expect me
to write you a letter, did you?</i>

640
00:37:46,640 --> 00:37:48,040
<i>I'm surprised too.</i>

641
00:37:48,680 --> 00:37:50,120
<i>It's obvious</i>

642
00:37:50,200 --> 00:37:51,560
<i>how difficult it is for someone</i>

643
00:37:51,640 --> 00:37:53,160
<i>who is bad at literature to write this,</i>

644
00:37:53,240 --> 00:37:54,440
<i>so don't laugh at me.</i>

645
00:37:56,480 --> 00:37:57,360
<i>Let me guess.</i>

646
00:37:57,440 --> 00:37:58,600
<i>When you are reading this,</i>

647
00:37:58,680 --> 00:38:01,080
<i>you should be preparing
your dorm living necessities.</i>

648
00:38:01,160 --> 00:38:02,000
<i>As for me,</i>

649
00:38:02,080 --> 00:38:03,480
<i>I should be at the airport already.</i>

650
00:38:06,200 --> 00:38:07,560
<i>I didn't tell any of you</i>

651
00:38:07,640 --> 00:38:09,120
<i>because I was afraid that when I saw you...</i>

652
00:38:15,480 --> 00:38:17,240
<i>I was afraid that when I saw you guys,</i>

653
00:38:17,320 --> 00:38:18,680
<i>I would be reluctant to leave.</i>

654
00:38:21,480 --> 00:38:22,920
<i>But you're different.</i>

655
00:38:23,000 --> 00:38:24,200
<i>You are so smart.</i>

656
00:38:24,280 --> 00:38:25,520
<i>When they get mad,</i>

657
00:38:25,600 --> 00:38:26,840
<i>you can help me calm them down.</i>

658
00:38:27,680 --> 00:38:29,920
<i>I picked up a quote from a movie
a few days ago.</i>

659
00:38:32,760 --> 00:38:34,640
<i>"All encounters in life</i>

660
00:38:34,720 --> 00:38:36,320
<i>are reunions after a long time apart.</i>

661
00:38:38,680 --> 00:38:40,440
<i>To put it simply,</i>

662
00:38:40,520 --> 00:38:41,800
<i>when I first met you guys,</i>

663
00:38:41,880 --> 00:38:43,440
<i>I knew we would get along well.</i>

664
00:38:43,960 --> 00:38:45,120
<i>My intuition has been proven</i>

665
00:38:45,200 --> 00:38:46,600
<i>to be spot-on.</i>

666
00:38:47,640 --> 00:38:50,480
<i>I remember when we got punished together
during military training,</i>

667
00:38:50,560 --> 00:38:52,200
<i>the trash that we searched together,</i>

668
00:38:53,080 --> 00:38:55,160
{\an8}<i>the sunrises, sunsets, fireworks, and snow</i>

669
00:38:55,240 --> 00:38:57,080
{\an8}<i>that we watched together,</i>

670
00:38:57,160 --> 00:38:59,880
<i>and three years of wishing each other
a Happy New Year.</i>

671
00:39:01,640 --> 00:39:03,880
<i>I'm happy that all of you
were part of my youth,</i>

672
00:39:03,960 --> 00:39:05,440
<i>but there is a saying.</i>

673
00:39:06,040 --> 00:39:08,080
{\an8}<i>"Life is like a train journey.</i>

674
00:39:08,160 --> 00:39:10,240
<i>Someone will get off at the station."</i>

675
00:39:10,320 --> 00:39:12,360
<i>Guan Fang chose economics.</i>

676
00:39:12,440 --> 00:39:14,280
<i>You're determined to study journalism.</i>

677
00:39:14,800 --> 00:39:16,880
<i>Su Zaizai and Lurang are finally together.</i>

678
00:39:17,920 --> 00:39:19,240
<i>It's so great.</i>

679
00:39:19,320 --> 00:39:21,280
<i>I believe everyone will one day</i>

680
00:39:21,360 --> 00:39:23,720
<i>meet somewhere higher in the future.</i>

681
00:39:27,040 --> 00:39:28,680
<i>I'm not worried about everyone else.</i>

682
00:39:29,280 --> 00:39:30,520
<i>I just think</i>

683
00:39:31,160 --> 00:39:34,200
<i>that you may look fearless,</i>

684
00:39:34,840 --> 00:39:36,320
<i>but you are quite timid sometimes.</i>

685
00:39:36,400 --> 00:39:38,160
<i>I'm sure you're very nervous
now that you're alone.</i>

686
00:39:39,880 --> 00:39:41,680
<i>Do you still remember what I said?</i>

687
00:39:41,760 --> 00:39:43,040
Just go.

688
00:39:44,040 --> 00:39:45,200
It's pretty dark up ahead.

689
00:39:45,280 --> 00:39:47,040
If you are afraid, you can call my name.

690
00:39:47,120 --> 00:39:48,800
My name will give you power.

691
00:39:53,440 --> 00:39:55,400
<i>I hope my best friends</i>

692
00:39:55,480 --> 00:39:56,840
<i>will be safe and happy,</i>

693
00:39:56,920 --> 00:39:58,160
<i>eat well, drink well,</i>

694
00:39:58,240 --> 00:40:00,080
<i>always get a good night's sleep,</i>

695
00:40:00,160 --> 00:40:01,400
<i>have plenty of choices,</i>

696
00:40:01,480 --> 00:40:03,280
<i>and meet friendly people.</i>

697
00:40:03,880 --> 00:40:05,520
<i>Even if we are miles apart,</i>

698
00:40:05,600 --> 00:40:07,120
<i>we will still shine brightly</i>

699
00:40:07,200 --> 00:40:08,600
<i>when we don't see each other.</i>

700
00:40:09,440 --> 00:40:11,320
TO JIANG JIA

701
00:40:12,080 --> 00:40:13,840
<i>Writing so much is not easy for me.</i>

702
00:40:14,440 --> 00:40:15,360
<i>That's all.</i>

703
00:40:16,240 --> 00:40:17,440
<i>If I write more,</i>

704
00:40:18,120 --> 00:40:19,480
<i>I might not bring myself to leave.</i>

705
00:40:20,800 --> 00:40:22,240
<i>Finally, let me confirm this again.</i>

706
00:40:23,200 --> 00:40:24,720
<i>No matter where I am,</i>

707
00:40:24,800 --> 00:40:27,840
<i>we will always be
each other's most important person, right?</i>

708
00:40:39,520 --> 00:40:40,960
<i>Are you taking it back?</i>

709
00:40:41,040 --> 00:40:43,320
<i>No, it just needs an update.</i>

710
00:40:49,760 --> 00:40:51,280
After all,

711
00:40:51,360 --> 00:40:53,480
I'm no longer your teacher, Ms. Su Zaizai.

712
00:40:55,880 --> 00:40:57,400
<i>Congratulations to Rangrang</i>

713
00:40:57,480 --> 00:40:59,360
<i>on having a girlfriend.</i>

714
00:40:59,440 --> 00:41:01,360
<i>I hope you'll cherish her</i>

715
00:41:01,440 --> 00:41:02,880
<i>and keep up the good work.</i>

716
00:41:02,960 --> 00:41:04,560
<i>Su Zaizai is pretty, generous,</i>

717
00:41:04,640 --> 00:41:05,840
<i>positive, and cute.</i>

718
00:41:05,920 --> 00:41:07,400
<i>She is the one and only</i>

719
00:41:07,480 --> 00:41:08,720
<i>for Zhang Lurang.</i>

720
00:41:11,320 --> 00:41:13,080
<i>Rangrang, you are blushing.</i>

721
00:41:13,840 --> 00:41:14,800
<i>I'm not.</i>

722
00:41:14,880 --> 00:41:16,480
<i>You clearly are.</i>

723
00:41:16,560 --> 00:41:17,400
<i>No, I'm not.</i>

724
00:41:17,480 --> 00:41:18,560
<i>See for yourself.</i>

725
00:41:21,800 --> 00:41:22,880
<i>You are blushing.</i>

726
00:41:25,160 --> 00:41:26,000
<i>Blushing.</i>

727
00:41:26,080 --> 00:41:28,320
Look at you.

728
00:41:28,400 --> 00:41:29,600
You are blushing.

729
00:41:30,240 --> 00:41:31,240
You're blushing.

730
00:41:31,720 --> 00:41:33,160
<i>I really envy Rangrang</i>

731
00:41:33,240 --> 00:41:34,840
<i>for having such a great girlfriend.</i>

732
00:41:34,920 --> 00:41:36,960
<i>Of course, it's all thanks to me.</i>
